{
  "id": "6a1e5356cddf96ee5c29b9ee",
  "title": "過当競争「憧れ産業」ライフサイクルをリボンモデル探索のフィルターにする",
  "created": 1780372313,
  "updated": 1780378761,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a1e5356cddf96ee5c29b9ee",
      "text": "過当競争「憧れ産業」ライフサイクルをリボンモデル探索のフィルターにする",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372313,
      "updated": 1780372313
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e534b00000000003d4f19",
      "text": "[tokoroten.icon]のClaudeとの会話から自動生成され記事です。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372314,
      "updated": 1780376208
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e628100000000003d4f71",
      "text": "美容師から「毎年、夢をあきらめた美容師が大量に生まれるので、常にとんでもない数のハサミがメルカリに出品されている」という話を聞いたのがキッカケ",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780376208,
      "updated": 1780376261
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e628900000000003d4f72",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780376216,
      "updated": 1780376216
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e535500000000003d4f1b",
      "text": "----",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372324,
      "updated": 1780372326
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f1e",
      "text": "[リクルート]型の[リボンモデル] (需要と供給の間に立つ二面マーケット) で",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372351
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f1f",
      "text": "新規ビジネスを発想するときの[* 探索フィルター]として、",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f20",
      "text": "「[過当競争]＝[憧れ産業]」を採用する。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372360
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f21",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f22",
      "text": "[*** 中核アイディア]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f23",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f24",
      "text": "[* 憧れで人が大量に流入 → 数年で大半が廃業 → また新規参入] という",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f25",
      "text": "[* 高速回転サイクル]が止まらない産業を狙う。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f26",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f27",
      "text": "サイクル上の各段階で同じパターンのニーズが反復するため、",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f28",
      "text": "データが蓄積でき、プラットフォーム化の余地がある。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f29",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f2a",
      "text": "code:code.text",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f2b",
      "text": " 夢を持った参入者",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f2c",
      "text": "   ↓",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f2d",
      "text": " 開業準備 (何を揃えればいいかわからない)     ← ニーズ①",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f2e",
      "text": "   ↓",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f2f",
      "text": " 集客がうまくいかない                       ← ニーズ②",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f30",
      "text": "   ↓",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f31",
      "text": " 利益が出ない / ノウハウなし                 ← ニーズ③",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f32",
      "text": "   ↓",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f33",
      "text": " 3年以内に半数以上が廃業                    ← ニーズ④",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f34",
      "text": "   ↓",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f35",
      "text": " 廃業処理 (設備・在庫の処分、原状回復)        ← ニーズ⑤",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f36",
      "text": "   ↓",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f37",
      "text": " 新規参入者がまた入ってくる (ループ)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f38",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f39",
      "text": "[*** 該当する産業の例]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f3a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f3b",
      "text": "\t[* 飲食店]: 3年以内廃業率 70%、5年で 80%+",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f3c",
      "text": "\t[* 美容室]: 1年以内 60% / 3年以内 90% 倒産と言われる",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f3d",
      "text": "\t[* パーソナルジム]: 開業 300〜500 万円 / 資格不要 / 1店舗あたり平均年商 1,800 万円 / M&A売却相場 250〜2,500 万円",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f3e",
      "text": "\t専門学校が活発だが就職率が低い「夢追い産業」 (動画・声優・イラスト・音楽・ファッション) — [* 過当競争の上流構造]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f3f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f40",
      "text": "[*** リボンモデルが成立する条件 (議論で抽出)]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f41",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f42",
      "text": "\t情報の非対称性が高い",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f43",
      "text": "\t既存の仲介者が弱いか「片手」で止まっている (例: 学習塾は塾ナビ等が多数あるが、SUUMO 型の真のマーケットプレイスではなく単なるリード・ジェネ)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f44",
      "text": "\tつないだ後にデータが蓄積できる",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f45",
      "text": "\t供給側が分散・零細で自力では集客できない",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f46",
      "text": "\t取引単価が大きすぎず小さすぎない",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f47",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f48",
      "text": "[*** 成立しなかった例 (反証)]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f49",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f4a",
      "text": "[* 鉄スクラップ業界] — 同じ「中小工場 × 業者」マッチングでもリボンが成立しない:",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f4b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f4c",
      "text": "\t中小工場には「困ったら近所のヤードに電話」で痛みがない",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f4d",
      "text": "\t価格は H2 相場でほぼ決まりコモディティ",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f4e",
      "text": "\tスクラップは重いので[* 輸送コストが勝負]を分け広域マッチング不要",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f4f",
      "text": "\t信頼関係が既に形成済み",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f50",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f51",
      "text": "→ 「価格が市場相場で決まる × 物流が重い × 既存の信頼関係」のときマッチング価値が消える。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f52",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f53",
      "text": "[*** アリババが中国で成立し日本で成立しない構造]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f54",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f55",
      "text": "中国 (2000年代): 「信頼できる仲介者不在 × 供給分散 × 需要が遠い」の三重課題",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f56",
      "text": "日本: [* [総合商社]が探索/信用/金融/物流/リスク/情報を全部アナログで提供] —",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780378761
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f57",
      "text": "アリババが1〜2をデジタル化したのに対し、商社は1〜6を高精度で提供している。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f58",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f59",
      "text": "商社モデル = [* 「リボンの真ん中で結んで終わり」ではなく「自らが結び目になる」]。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f5a",
      "text": "B2B 取引が関係性で動く日本ではプラットフォームでは代替されにくい。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e536400000000003d4f5b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372340,
      "updated": 1780372340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e535700000000003d4f1d",
      "text": "----",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372326,
      "updated": 1780372430
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e534c00000000003d4f1a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1780372315,
      "updated": 1780372315
    }
  ]
}